{"tid":2093324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人覺得感情係大於新鮮感","createTime":"2020-07-03T18:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T14:08:33.000Z","uid":192075,"like":118,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1afd73f7ef3eb5c4ec296d825c212e5783dc284c","tid":2093324,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"好奇怪<br />\n係咪我思想太old school?<br />\n<br />\n由細到大一向覺得感情會因為時間而變厚<br />\n好難有嘢打破<br />\n除非其中一方衰到貼地，例如家暴呀，偷食呀之類<br />\n正正常常一段感情應該係會行到尾<br />\n<br />\n但係唔知幾時開始發覺<br />\n一對情侶，就算另一半幾正常都好<br />\n都係會因為新鮮感而發生好多事<br />\n<br />\n究竟係個風氣有問題<br />\n定我呢個思想有問題呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />風氣有問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個思想有問題"},{"pid":"ffdb69823489553f1cf2d83e77b630113666af7d","tid":2093324,"uid":38904,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"你嘅感情建基於欣賞對方嘅優點<br />\n人哋嘅感情建基於新鮮感<br />\n冇contradict <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bdb16f4528a10f49e9e59e3483b2ff81bc8fc2","tid":2093324,"uid":36158,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"唔需要二元論<br />\n可以風氣同埋你思想都無問題<br />\n<br />\n另外新鮮感亦都可以as a function of 感情  (e.g深左感情可以玩屎眼)<br />\n感情可以as a function of 新鮮感 (e.g 玩完屎眼感情好左)"},{"pid":"4b4e0043a204a668f9f8544022f78eed85d11281","tid":2093324,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffdb69823489553f1cf2d83e77b630113666af7d","tid":2093324,"uid":38904,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"你嘅感情建基於欣賞對方嘅優點<br />\n人哋嘅感情建基於新鮮感<br />\n冇contradict <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"咁要搵到幾耐<br />\n先知大家無抵觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602bb12b2ae00a7a65a6432157ee69b41654cb94","tid":2093324,"uid":192075,"like":2,"dislik